TEACH RC_BUTTONS                              Aaron Sloman 6 May 1997

LIB RC_BUTTONS

A library built on top of RC_LINEPIC to provide mouse sensitive
buttons in graphical windows, either to provide information or to
provide extra control.

For a general overview of the graphical facilities see HELP RCLIB.

For detailed information on the button facilities see
    HELP RC_BUTTONS

The previous version of this teach file is now defunct.

For a tutorial introduction to the facilities used in LIB RC_BUTTONS
see
    TEACH RC_LINEPIC


